00:38:34.910 --> 00:38:36.880
Now, Furst-- Furst
is the company

00:38:36.880 --> 00:38:41.911
who made the first Mozart
Kugel-- they use squares.

00:38:41.911 --> 00:38:43.410
I claim they're a
little bit better.

00:38:43.410 --> 00:38:48.840
But interesting question is,
which uses more material?

00:38:48.840 --> 00:38:50.160
Something to think about.

00:38:50.160 --> 00:38:56.430
Meanwhile-- I won't
torture you more by eating.

00:38:59.400 --> 00:39:01.000
All right.

00:39:01.000 --> 00:39:02.470
So this is a Mozart
Kugel problem.

